data.description: Welcome to your charming home in the heart of St. Pete! This three-bedroom, one-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, making it the ideal place to call home. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful luxury vinyl floors that not only add a touch of elegance but also make maintenance a breeze. The inviting living room features a wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings and creating lasting memories. Crown molding in the living room adds a touch of sophistication to the space. The kitchen features an abundance of cabinets for all your storage needs and ample countertop space for meal preparation. The matching appliances add a sleek and cohesive look to the room. Ceiling fans are thoughtfully placed throughout the home to keep you comfortable year-round. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide space for family and guests, while the bathroom is both functional and stylish. One of the standout features of this property is the huge backyard with alley access, making it perfect for boat storage or providing endless opportunities for outdoor activities and entertainment. Great upgrades include a 2017 AC, roof, and water heater, ensuring your peace of mind for years to come. The house was also replumbed just three years ago, further enhancing its value. Location is key, and this home delivers! A short drive will take you to the vibrant Downtown St. Pete area, where you can explore a variety of local restaurants, breweries, shopping options, sports venues, parks, and more. Easy access to nearby interstates ensures convenient travel throughout the region. Don't miss your chance to own this lovely St. Pete home. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect place to start creating your own unforgettable memories. This gem won't last long!
